elect name=year><option value=2004>2004</option><option value=2005 selected>2005</option></select> <input type=submit value=Go></form><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Thu 08 Dec 2005</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="13275"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Phone and Chat Support Closed Today</span><br><span class="feat"><a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/forums/b1/93575706">[Post A Comment]</a> - <a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=13275>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=13275">Mail News</a></span><br>Phone and Chat support closed on Thursday December 8th 2005<br><br>Phone and Chat support will be unavailable on Thursday December 8th 2005. You can still submit a new technical or account support incident using the form at http://www.station.sony.com/email, or search the customer service Knowledgebase at http://www.station.sony.com/kb<br><br>Phone and Chat support will return at their normal hours on Friday December 9th 2005. Phone support is normally available Monday through Friday 9:00am through 1:30pm PST and again 3:30 through 6:00pm PST. Chat support is normally available Monday through Friday 9:00am through 6:00pm PST.<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Kwill">Kwill</a> @ Thu 08 Dec 2005</span><br><br><br><a name="13274"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Patch December 8</span><br><span class="feat"><a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/forums/b1/93575691">[Post A Comment]</a> - <a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=13274>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=13274">Mail News</a></span><br>As reported yesterday, this patch should fix some of the problems players encountered after the December 7th patch.  The downtime is three hours.<br><br>Patch message:<br><br>December 8th, 2005<br>_____________________<br><br><br>*** Events <br><br>- The holiday event will now allow a full group to partake instead of just 1 person.<br>- The Lower Guk and Freeport monster missions will now properly drop Shards of Wisdom.<br>- /dzadd has been fixed and should work properly again.<br><br>*** Items ***<br>- Some of Archaeologist Flottwit’s items were missing augmentation slots and spell effects. In addition, some of the items now have a lower required or recommended level.<br>- A small sample of bags that were incorrectly giving an error message that you were not the right class to use it as a tradeskill container have been fixed.<br>- Dreadspire invitations are now properly persistent.<br><br>*** NPCS ***<br><br><br>- Commander Cogswain has returned to Lavastorm.<br><br>- The EverQuest Team<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Kwill">Kwill</a> @ Thu 08 Dec 2005</span><br><br><br><img src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Wed 07 Dec 2005</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="13260"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Post-patch Patch Tonight</span><br><span class="feat"><a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/forums/b1/93567040">[Post A Comment]</a> - <a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=13260>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=13260">Mail News</a></span><br>A couple of things are going to be fixed with a patch tonight, including the holiday events and /dzadd, which is not working at the present time.<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Kwill">Kwill</a> @ Wed 07 Dec 2005</span><br><br><br><a name="13259"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Legends Service To Be Discontinued</span><br><span class="feat"><a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/forums/b1/93566797">[Post A Comment]</a> - <a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=13259>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=13259">Mail News</a></span><br>EQLive has posted that the premium Legends service will be discontinued as of February 1, 2006.<br><br>The Legends service is offered on the Stormhammer server.  The letter states that it has not been decided whether Stormhammer will become a regular server or players will be moved to other existing servers.  The letter states the decision will be partly up to the community.  A poll will be posted shortly in game that will allow subscribers to choose whether Stormhammer will be shut down or kept as a regular server.<br><br>Stormhammer has been floundering for population for quite some time now.  This decision will probably come as no surprise to the players who subscribe to the premium service, which promised more GM attention and more events on the server for a higher subscription fee.<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Kwill">Kwill</a> @ Wed 07 Dec 2005</span><br><br><br><a name="13258"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Comments on Holiday Events</span><br><span class="feat"><a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/forums/b1/93566643">[Post A Comment]</a> - <a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=13258>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=13258">Mail News</a></span><br>The holiday events have a problem:  the shared task given out by MC Tinkerton actually only gives one person the task, instead of the group.<br><br>Oshran wrote: "The fact that only one player in a group can have the mission at a time is not intended.  This should be a normal group task where up to 6 players can work together.  The problem is already fixed on test and should be fixed on the live servers asap (likely within the next few days)."<br><br>Kytherea posted later in the thread on EQLive "This should be fixed tonight."<br><br>People also were irritated that anyone can loot the chests that spawn from completing the task.<br><br>Kytherea posted, "There should be multiple chests spawning as a result of completing this event, and yes the chests are available to everyone."<br><br>Oshran commented on EQLive:<br><br>"The party favor chests that spawn on mission complete are for anyone in the area.  Think of it as a piñata.  The New Year gemstones (which are much nicer than anything you'll find in the free party favor chests) go only to the individual(s) who complete the quest. "<br><br>Some people complained that the Bristlebane Party Platter prize was unfair to tradeskillers who worked hard to get the skill to make this item.<br><br>Rashere added:<br><br><blockquote>The  [Bristlebane's Party Platter] BBPP (neat acryonym) is only a 2% spawn chance on the chests.  It's the uber-rare best of the best present the machine gives out.<br> <br>As to the FFA loot...its a holiday event.  Sharing, caring, feel good happiness...the party machine is spreading joy and presents to everyone around when someone finishes the quest.  The person who actually completes the event gets a totally different prize.</blockquote><br><br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Kwill">Kwill</a> @ Wed 07 Dec 2005</span><br><br><br><a name="13257"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">EQ Platinum Now Available</span><br><span class="feat"><a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/forums/b1/93566376">[Post A Comment]</a> - <a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=13257>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=13257">Mail News</a></span><br>Just in time for the holidays -- EQ Platinum, the EverQuest set up through Gates of Discord, is available for $19.99 via <a href="https://store.station.sony.com/digitalDistribution/base/detail.jsp?SKU=EQPLT-DD-SW1005-EQPLAT">digital download</a>.  It should also be available as a retail box.<br><br>This makes starting the game or coming back after being gone for a while very reasonable in terms of cost and convenience.<br><br>To buy the remaing expansions, including Omens of War, Dragons of Norrath, and Depths of Darkhollow, sold separately, is $60.  All are available as a digital download as well.<br><br>The entire set of complete EQ expansions therefore will total $80.  What a great gift!<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Kwill">Kwill</a> @ Wed 07 Dec 2005</span><br><br><br><a name="13253"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Monster Mission Shards</span><br><span class="feat"><a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/forums/b1/93557729">[Post A Comment]</a> - <a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=13253>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=13253">Mail News</a></span><br>Now that the monster missions require all group members to loot a shard to get experience, there has been some question about where the shards might be found.  Rashere posted today on EQLive, "The shards can come from anything in the mission, but in general you will find them in the same place as the artifact loot."<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Kwill">Kwill</a> @ Wed 07 Dec 2005</span><br><br><br><a name="13245"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Patch Message December 7</span><br><span class="feat"><a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/forums/b1/93551955">[Post A Comment]</a> - <a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=13245>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=13245">Mail News</a></span><br>Some of the highlights are below.  The biggest change in today's patch was to the Monster Missions.  No more free /afk experience and less overall experience, too:<br><br>- Monster Mission experience now properly takes into account hell level modifiers. These modifiers smooth out the experience curve to lessen the impact of the old hell levels (30, 35, 40, and 45). Inclusion of these modifiers in the monster experience will cause you to gain more experience than before during hell levels, essentially returning it to a normal level, but you will gain slightly less experience than before when you are not on a hell level. <br><br>- Within Monster Missions, you will now find Shards of Wisdom that will impart upon you the experiences of the creature you inhabit at the time. Looting one of these shards will grant the experience to your main character upon successful completion of the mission.<br><br><br>~ Holiday Festival ~<br><br>M.C. Tinkerton needs help repairing his Clockwork Party Machine in time to celebrate 3199! The party machine's dance gyroscopes, firework cannons and party favor dispensers are fully functional, but the most important piece, the machine's primary party motivator, was stolen at the zero hour. M.C. Tinkerton seeks adventurers to steal back the primary party motivator from the Dark Mistletoe giants, a grouchy clan of frost giant nomads in the Great Divide. Seek out M.C. Tinkerton in the Plane of Knowledge for further details.<br><br>- Archaeologist Flottwit has uncovered a cache of older Darkhollow items and is currently searching the bazaar for some of the newer items for comparison. If you have a Depths of Darkhollow item that changed from tradeable to no trade with the last patch and you'd prefer to have the old tradeable item instead, give the no trade version to Flottwit and he'll give you the old tradeable item in return. Flottwit will only be around until the next patch.<br><br><br>~ New Arena ~<br><br>A new arena zone is now available off of Lake Rathe!<br><br>The entire patch message is below.<br><p><a href="fullstory.php?id=13245">Read More...</a><br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Kwill">Kwill</a> @ Wed 07 Dec 2005</span><br><br><br><img src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Tue 06 Dec 2005</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="13218"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Patch Tomorrow</span><br><span class="feat"><a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/forums/b1/93530003">[Post A Comment]</a> - <a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=13218>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=13218">Mail News</a></span><br>All EverQuest servers will be coming down at 4:00 AM PST (-8 UTC) on Wednesday 12/07/2005 for an update. Estimated downtime is 8 hours.<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Kwill">Kwill</a> @ Tue 06 Dec 2005</span><br><br><br><img src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Sun 04 Dec 2005</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="13165"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Live Update:  Wednesday December 7</span><br><span class="feat"><a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/forums/b1/93489069">[Post A Comment]</a> - <a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=13165>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=13165">Mail News</a></span><br>There will be a patch and an update on December 7.  Kytherea writes:<br><br>"Yes there is an update this month, in fact it is scheduled for next week on Wednesday, December 7th.  There will be holiday events this month as well which should also start with this update."<br><br>Holiday events sound fun!<br> <br><br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Kwill">Kwill</a> @ Sun 04 Dec 2005</span><br><br><br><img src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://vnmedia.ign.com/eqvault.ign.com/skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--></center>
